{"tid":467842,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"真係好頂唔順啲人口臭","createTime":"2017-11-14T00:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-14T11:43:31.000Z","uid":157977,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"95530135057adcc4707d291d5f461fe9c9aa61f5","tid":467842,"uid":157977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T00:59:05.000Z","msg":"真係求其呼啖氣都臭到人暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我有個同事又係口臭, 臭咗幾年都冇改善, 點解冇人話佢知呢個問題架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e011540e9647e85b7cfc1bd445670ff4e07838","tid":467842,"uid":157977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:01:30.000Z","msg":"有時搭巴士隔離個阿叔口臭都好大獲, 打個喊露即刻臭到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0da67790744ca1ef7369d1662f04f36b0dc050","tid":467842,"uid":111929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:17:10.000Z","msg":"以前中學有個同學把口又係勁臭 我地背後偷偷笑佢係咪飲開石油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成陣gas味"},{"pid":"288d8df69b9b04f92c23441dade97f9bf5db8d33","tid":467842,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:17:17.000Z","msg":"自己話自己口臭，買啲爽浪大家食"},{"pid":"f3b6853f0ee9123fd953eafce15bd7af8dc6e95b","tid":467842,"uid":151421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:17:32.000Z","msg":"你都無話佢知啦。出黎做野邊有咁好死提人，又唔知對方點諗。"},{"pid":"1e247322a33575ca245845d1e72960dd0169c5a2","tid":467842,"uid":9880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:24:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己話自己口臭，買啲爽浪大家食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我試過買埋請埋條臭口祖食, 佢話唔食呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22037991798f47de863b1df696c11672c3f8c93d","tid":467842,"uid":91259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl